35#include "mech_locl.h"
36
37GSSAPI_LIB_FUNCTION OM_uint32 GSSAPI_LIB_CALL
38gss_inquire_sec_context_by_oid (OM_uint32 *minor_status,
39 gss_const_ctx_id_t context_handle,
40 const gss_OID desired_object,
41 gss_buffer_set_t *data_set)
42{
43 struct _gss_context *ctx = (struct _gss_context *) context_handle;
44 OM_uint32 major_status;
45 gssapi_mech_interface m;
46
47 *minor_status = 0;
48 *data_set = GSS_C_NO_BUFFER_SET;
49 if (ctx == NULL)
50 return GSS_S_NO_CONTEXT;
51
52 /*
53 * select the approprate underlying mechanism routine and
54 * call it.
55 */
56
57 m = ctx->gc_mech;
58
59 if (m == NULL)
60 return GSS_S_BAD_MECH;
61
62 if (m->gm_inquire_sec_context_by_oid != NULL) {
63 major_status = m->gm_inquire_sec_context_by_oid(minor_status,
64 ctx->gc_ctx, desired_object, data_set);
65 if (major_status != GSS_S_COMPLETE)
66 _gss_mg_error(m, major_status, *minor_status);
67 } else
68 major_status = GSS_S_BAD_MECH;
69
70 return major_status;
71}
